org.apache.lucene.mockfile

Class DisableFsyncFS

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.spi.FileSystemProvider
      • org.apache.lucene.mockfile.FilterFileSystemProvider
        • org.apache.lucene.mockfile.DisableFsyncFS

  • public class DisableFsyncFS
extends FilterFileSystemProvider
    Disables actual calls to fsync.

    All other filesystem operations are passed thru as normal.
